column5: Sounds like with all the problems you deserved a great day of fishing on the water.  It seems you got that and more... even with the waves!  Great Post!  Cheers  Jen

WOW....great catch man,  you guys did amazing,and you guys stuck it out considering all that happened,and it looked pretty rough as well,and it paid off with all those great looking fish,and gotta love those walleyes ,thanks for sharing your trip and those awsome fish pics....cheers
sounds like a good day to me.  looks windy. great fishing bro!

Thanks guys. Glad to be back and I am looking forward to reading and submitting more reports!  Its going to be a toughie figuring out where to fish the opener though. So many lakes , so little time!!!!
